cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this software, please cite both the software and the accompanying paper."
title: "Generating-Element Maximum Entropy: reproducibility code"
repository-code: "https://github.com/SZabolotnii/Ku-MaxEnt-code-supplement"
url: "https://github.com/SZabolotnii/Ku-MaxEnt-code-supplement"
abstract: >-
  Verification code (base R) for the paper "Generating-Element Maximum
  Entropy for Non-Gaussian Uncertainty Evaluation".
  Reproduces all four numerical experiments: heavy-tailed (Cauchy)
  reconstruction, bimodal-mixture reconstruction, the generating-element /
  tail-class matching study, and the M&V sampling-design optimization.
type: software
authors:
