version: "1.0.0"
date-released: "2026-06-13"
license: MIT
keywords:
  - maximum entropy
  - generating element
  - Kunchenko decomposition space
  - PATP
  - heavy-tailed distributions
  - measurement uncertainty
  - GUM
references:
